    {
        "text": "Among all the places in Vietnam that I traveled to,  a serene yet captivating mountain town up northwest of Vietnam named Sapa is the only place that, at least I fell in love with. Situated in Lao Cai Province, 380 km northwest of Hanoi, Sapa is famous with its rugged scenery, rice terraces, and the people. Trekking in Sapa Vietnam is one of the way to see the beautiful rice terraces and meet the minority ethnics.", 
