    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 5, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "Most probably you will start from Hanoi. There are two ways that you can choose to get to Sapa, by train or by bus . There are pros and cons for sure in each of the way. I took direct sleeper bus from Hanoi to Sapa. Not the most comfy ride but it\u2019s cheap and arrived straight in Sapa to start the trekking.", 
