        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "Bus from Hanoi to Sapa. Approximately 6 hours ride and it costs around VND 260,000 \u2013 450,000 depending on the services and the comfort of the bus. The time table may varies from 6.30 a.m., 12 p.m., and 10 p.m. (Make sure again by asking hostel/hotel reception).", 
