        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "Train from Hanoi to Lao Cai, continued by bus or private car to Sapa. The train journey takes around 8 hours. There are two train operators: Vietnam Railways and the luxury tourist train. Vietnam Railways has different seatings from normal seat to sleeper berth. Price varies from VND 155,000 \u2013 400,000. There are two departures, around 8 p.m. and 10 p.m. After arriving in Lao Cai, you can take bus to Sapa which takes around one hour and costs around VND 100,000.", 
